Enum Mode backed by u8 has idle be 0; active be 1.

Packed layout record Header has mode: Mode; code: u8.

To main, giving i32.
Let bytes be buffer of 2 u8 filled with 0.
Let header be Header with mode be Mode.active and code be 9.
Write header into bytes at 0.
Give (bytes at 0 as i32) plus (bytes at 1 as i32).
